Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人与人是靠邂逅而联系在一起的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友的朋友是朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一直连下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能整个AQUA的人都变成朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美了太美了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里的美妙引擎全开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级FULL POWER的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个季节吹拂过城市的风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上了淡淡的草帽气息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天来到了新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而夏天是一年中最佳的观光季节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小镇中的人渐渐变多 开始热闹起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉小镇生机勃勃的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.40,0:00:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天又洗了好多衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为天气很好 就决定一块洗掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 这是大叔的内裤 很大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 小姑娘 早上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的腰怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能尽情享受散步了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.77,0:01:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈好像有很多认识的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.99,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那些 充满温情的街道与人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来比我们两个本地人还要多呢 您觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸭肉炖饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(346,440)}{\fs20}risotto
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是送的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前段时间的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 是香草沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样太不好意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:04:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次你教我把剪刀吊在屋顶上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能找到失物的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了它 你看 我找到我跟先生的纪念物了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我才应该谢谢你的沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里的店员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是问那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跟灯里前辈究竟是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…平时会聊聊天…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 我们还没自我介绍过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却可以那么亲密…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级不可思议的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了 等会我要离开一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你走开的话 下午的练习怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我想去布拉诺岛买点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆我们也取消下午的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟在灯里后面看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 为什么要这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想知道灯里不跟我们在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎么结识朋友的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样或许能解开灯里前辈不为人知的秘密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vaporetto？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是水上巴士的码头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了 请给我两张全票
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你船票
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用说目的地吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为Vaporetto无论坐到哪都是一个价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非蓝华前辈从来没坐过水上巴士？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米有！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代步工具只有凤尾舟 那是领航员的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀～听我说完嘛 小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经变得很暖和了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 外出也没这么难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 声音这么大 速度却这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮的花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人她认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次看到这种花 香味也很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个叫四照花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四照花？这个名字真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请坐请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 小姐你先请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 还是您先请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐请坐请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪也来坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好 亚利亚社长 我这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就形成了一个小群体呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家应该都是初次见面的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到哪去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:08:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去奶奶家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去布拉诺岛买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去超级亲密的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说啊 我们看上去会不会很傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咋了 咋了 咋咋咋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是到站了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都要撞上去才停啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是常识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水上巴士真是让人昏昏欲睡的交通工具啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点适应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈不可思议的秘密能解开吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她又没有做什么特别的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉啊…有点犯困了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咋了 咋了 咋咋咋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟你说 是到站了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西还真是适应不了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闲适而怀旧 又有点呆呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说灯里前辈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说水上巴士啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时一个不注意 就会被「哇」地吓一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说水上巴士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说灯里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的皮箱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮箱里面放的 说不定是尸体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是昨天看的侦探小说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人跟书里的尸体搬运人一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过是…说说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝…蓝华前辈 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她连那个人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不到啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在询问关于皮箱的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级危险的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自来熟并不是不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不能随便对谁都那样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不是应该过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 前辈说不定会被卷入什么事件的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 好 那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜…难道就不能安安静静地停船吗 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我们马上帮你捡起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小后辈 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了 姫社长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 全都捡起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 妨碍各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 真是不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体男也不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级危机的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…噪音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 到了下一站马上转回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只能到处找找看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 那我们兵分两路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那10分钟后在这里集合 记住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到亚利亚社长的声音了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我也听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 是这边没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有相信自己的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FIGHT 蓝华前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得走这边对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 灯里那家伙真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛不留下点记号啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像超级正确的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:16:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 好像在哪里看到过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也这么觉得…真不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣 好像活的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:17:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…我以前见过那个人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 蓝华前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是说 我也能玩这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 选哪个好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐也会让人偶跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次玩 不过我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊…小时候我看过的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…记起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人偶和旅行的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟邻居的孩子一起去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是很快乐的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 你看你看 好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 快看 真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果灯里没跟那个人熟络起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都不会发现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还一直把人家当做尸体搬运人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾随着灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能与自己遗忘的过去邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是难以想像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透过灯里这个滤光片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能看到原本看不到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫不起眼的东西也会开始闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 灯里就是这么一个奇妙的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级同感的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她又结识了一个朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我似乎明白为何灯里前辈有这么多朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 我玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 希望以后还会再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩怎么在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级偶遇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说自己是云游四方的人偶剧师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几年前还来过这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 话说回来啊 你的购物计划呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再去吧 因为今天得到了美丽的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 今天也是充满了美丽邂逅的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.12,0:22:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐的身边总会聚集着暖洋洋的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然会和蓝华姐姐与爱丽丝姐姐偶遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…那真的是偶遇吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些 珍贵的光芒中…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:58.13,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:11.11,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:26.16,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:38.97,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:38.97,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:45.31,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:52.92,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:03:00.39,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.93,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:10.70,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:58.13,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗际
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:11.11,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}洒落在 舒睡的睫毛间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:26.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}让轻拂的风吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:38.97,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}枝叶间滑落的阳光 映衬你的睡颜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:38.97,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:45.31,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}虽是个平凡无奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:52.92,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艳丽的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:03:00.39,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是与你邂逅的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.93,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:10.70,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}因为 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:56.19,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}白い帽子 追いかけて笑う 響く声は高く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:23:07.73,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}少し早い 夏の訪れに 耳を澄ましたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:15.64,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ゆっくりと 長くなる影ふたつ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:20.68,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}小さな 足音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:27.02,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}金色に煌めく 夕暮れる空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:32.72,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}波打ち際どこまでも染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:38.83,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}廻りだす季節の かけらを集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.96,0:23:44.30,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そっと触れた指先に感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:49.64,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}あふれる光の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:56.19,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}追逐着 白色帽子的笑声 响彻云际
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:23:07.73,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}倾听着 过早到来的 夏日之声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:15.64,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 拉长的两个影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:20.68,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}细碎的 脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:27.02,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}夕阳西下的天空 闪烁着耀眼的金色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:32.72,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}映照在波浪间染遍全城
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:38.83,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}细心收集不断变换的 季节的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.96,0:23:44.30,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}蓦然掠过指尖的感触
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:49.64,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}消失在泛起的光芒中
